      "message": "Line 139: 🟡 `notifPermissionPromptShown` is not persisted across configuration changes (e.g., screen rotation). Since `onCreate` is called again after a config change and `savedInstanceState` is not used to restore this flag, the permission check will re-run after rotation. Consider saving/restoring this in `onSaveInstanceState`/`onCreate` via the bundle, or moving the check into a ViewModel.",
